[30;1m32 | [0m[35mclass Pipeline(BaseAction[Dict[str, Any], Dict[str, Any]]):[0m

[30;1m34 | [0m[35m    Pipeline is a sequentially executed chain composed of multiple actions,[0m

[30;1m36 | [0m[35m    any given moment, the Pipeline retains the id of the currently executing[0m

[30;1m38 | [0m[35m    in progress. By registering an EventHandler, user can listen to events[0m

[30;1m242 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m244 | [0m[35m    key and secret key, sdk will automatically refresh the access token for you.[0m
